      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n\nUsers should be able to:\n\nsignup/login\nsearch events\nfilter by city/language/type\nview theaters & shows\nselect seats\nlock seats temporarily\nmake payment\ndownload ticket\ncancel booking\nrate/review event\n\nAdmins should:\n\ncreate events\ncreate shows\nconfigure pricing\nmanage screens/layouts",
